{"id":"jeshua","term":"Jeshua","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(1.) Head of the ninth priestly order (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 2:36\">Ezra 2:36</a>); called also Jeshuah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 24:11\">1 Chr. 24:11</a>).</p>\n<p>(2.) A Levite appointed by Hezekiah to distribute offerings in the priestly cities (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 31:15\">2 Chr. 31:15</a>).</p>\n<p>(3.) <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 2:6\">Ezra 2:6</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 7:11\">Neh. 7:11</a>.</p>\n<p>(4.) <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 2:40\">Ezra 2:40</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 7:43\">Neh. 7:43</a>.</p>\n<p>(5.) The son of Jozadak, and high priest of the Jews under Zerubbabel (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 7:7\">Neh. 7:7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 12:1\">12:1</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 12:7\">7</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 12:10\">10</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 12:26\">26</a>); called Joshua (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Haggai 1:1\">Hag. 1:1</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 1:12\">12</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 2:2\">2:2</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 2:4\">4</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Zechariah 3:1\">Zech. 3:1</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Zechariah 3:3\">3</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Zechariah 3:6\">6</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Zechariah 3:8\">8</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Zechariah 3:9\">9</a>).</p>\n<p>(6.) A Levite (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 8:33\">Ezra 8:33</a>).</p>\n<p>(7.) <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 3:19\">Neh. 3:19</a>.</p>\n<p>(8.) A Levite who assisted in the reformation under Nehemiah (8:7; 9:4, 5).</p>\n<p>(9.) Son of Kadmiel (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 12:24\">Neh. 12:24</a>).</p>\n<p>(10.) A city of Judah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 11:26\">Neh. 11:26</a>).</p>\n<p>(11.) <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 8:17\">Neh. 8:17</a>; Joshua, the son of Nun.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Ezra 2:36","1 Chronicles 24:11","2 Chronicles 31:15","Ezra 2:6","Nehemiah 7:11","Ezra 2:40","Nehemiah 7:43","Nehemiah 7:7","Nehemiah 12:1","Nehemiah 12:7","Nehemiah 12:10","Nehemiah 12:26","Haggai 1:1","Genesis 1:12","Genesis 2:2","Genesis 2:4","Zechariah 3:1","Zechariah 3:3","Zechariah 3:6","Zechariah 3:8","Zechariah 3:9","Ezra 8:33","Nehemiah 3:19","Nehemiah 12:24","Nehemiah 11:26","Nehemiah 8:17"]}